{"data":[{"date":"10:08 16/07","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 'k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u' \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/7, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn l\u00e0 v\u1eady song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn khi ghi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Diogo v\u00e0 Th\u1ebf V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Van Sy\" title=\"HLV V\u0103n S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n theo nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e2u b\u00f3ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00eam cho c\u00e1c em. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 s\u1ec7t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi thua tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng S\u1ef9 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i m\u01b0a gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng con c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 l\u00e0 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3&rdquo;, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng khi h\u01a1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day.JPEG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea7m t\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u01a1i \u0111i s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4251","checkdouble":"191331"},{"date":"10:26 16/07","title":"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/12/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chu\u1ed1i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CLB SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/HLV-Nguyen-Duc-Thang-bi-soc-khi-SLNA-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV SLNA, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebb chia\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, sai s\u00f3t hay c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung, lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, SLNA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm l\u00e0 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4250","checkdouble":"191332"},{"date":"09:24 16/07","title":"Mbappe nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi Real Madrid sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/mbappe-nhan-gui-real-madrid-sau-khi-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf PSG c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</span>, trong khi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Kylian Mbappe c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Mbappe \u1edf Real Madrid sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Mbappe \u1edf Real Madrid sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/mbappe-nhan-gui-real-madrid-sau-khi-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng r\u00f5 ngay sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u0103ng quang th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tu\u1ed5i, Mbappe c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t s\u1ed1t trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain t\u1eeb Monaco v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, thi\u00ean t\u00e0i tu\u1ed5i teen n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n g\u1eaft gao b\u1edfi CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 mang tin bu\u1ed3n cho Real Madrid, anh n\u00f3i: \u201cReal Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 cho m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sang \u0111\u00f3 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i 100% b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn l\u00e2u d\u00e0i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-thai-tu-mbappe-da-san-sang-ke-vi-421-191299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-thai-tu-mbappe-da-san-sang-ke-vi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-thai-tu-mbappe-da-san-sang-ke-vi-421-191299.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u201cTh\u00e1i t\u1eed\u201d Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u1ebf v\u1ecb</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng vua \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4249","checkdouble":"191317"},{"date":"09:06 16/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/nong-real-tien-rat-gan-thuong-vu-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T B\u1ec9, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Nong-Thuong-vu-Courtois-toi-Real-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018. Sau 7 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 27 pha c\u1ee9u thua &ndash; th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi ba tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Anh (v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 tranh HC \u0111\u1ed3ng). M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Brazil v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Courtois th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Keylor Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd sang tu\u1ed5i 32 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Los Blancos trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi Madrid. V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd b\u00e1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, Het Laatste Nieuws \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t c\u00f3 35 tri\u1ec7u euro trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Courtois s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 11 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a t\u1ea1i Bernabeu sau khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t ngay trong th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4248","checkdouble":"191318"},{"date":"09:23 16/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 4 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/chelsea-sap-chao-don-4-tan-binh-duoi-thoi-sarri.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd s\u1edbm cho ra m\u1eaft th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/chelsea-sap-chao-don-4-tan-binh-duoi-thoi-sarri.PNG\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Sarri s\u1eafp mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 v\u1ef1c d\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd mua s\u1eafm tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean mang t\u00ean Jorginho, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Sarri v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, Alfredo Pedulla ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00ec trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ebfn 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn, bao g\u1ed3m: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker c\u1ee7a AS Roma, trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady b\u1edfi Pedulla c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u00f4ng tin The Blues b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ea3 4 tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Hazard \u2013 Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp sang Real, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata-172-191241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata-172-191241.html\">M\u1edbi t\u1edbi Chelsea, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d th\u1eddi Conte</span><br>\r\nHLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u0169...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u201cv\u00f2i v\u0129nh\u201d Chelsea</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4247","checkdouble":"191319"},{"date":"09:50 16/07","title":"Mourinho mong m\u1ecfi sao s\u00e1ng Croatia s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/mourinho-len-tieng-hy-vong-sao-sang-croatia-se-gia-nhap-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ivan Perisic trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-HLV-Mourinho-muon-MU-chieu-mo-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh t\u1eeb Inter Milan. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Russia Today, HLV Mourinho v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 anh v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ivan Perisic? Anh \u1ea5y \u0111i t\u1eeb Croatia \u0111\u1ebfn Borussia, Dortmund, Wolfburg r\u1ed3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Inter Milan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Man United khi t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n anh \u1ea5y\",\u00a0HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi khen n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Perisic: \u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y. Nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t quen thu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta hay n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. V\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u00e0 Perisic c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. C\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e8 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Mario Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Inter. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y cho Perisic.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, ph\u00eda M.U mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng (50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) c\u1ee7a 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia Matteo Darmian cho Inter \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perisic ngay trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Roy Keane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\">Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa. Th\u00f4ng tin MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua Gareth...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4246","checkdouble":"191324"},{"date":"20:06 15/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/ronaldo-suyt-toi-napoli-thay-vi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo su\u00fdt t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch De Laurentiis. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Napoli kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef \u201cti\u1ec1n\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Real Madrid sang Juventus tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u00dd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh nhen nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i sau khi d\u00ednh l\u00edu t\u1edbi thu\u1ebf m\u00e1 t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Los Blancos h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. Sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League, CR7 l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Real v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo su\u00fdt t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo su\u00fdt t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Tiet-lo-Ronaldo-suyt-toi-Napoli-thay-vi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. HLV Massimiliano Allegri c\u1ee7a Juventus th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi anh l\u00e0 \u201c\u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng cho Juve, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00fang ra ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Napoli</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo su\u00fdt t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis. \u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o l\u00fac d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a CR7 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Turin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Napoli l\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" title=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/ronaldo-suyt-toi-napoli-thay-vi-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo su\u00fdt t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Laurentiis kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ronaldo s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp m\u00e0 Juventus chi ra \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u201cRonaldo c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Napoli\u201d, De Laurentiis n\u00f3i v\u1edbi La Repubblica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJorge Mendes, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c thu nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 350 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u01a1ng) l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fa \u0111\u1edfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CLB ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng anh ghi 5 b\u00e0n sau 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t khi ch\u01a1i cho Real. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd sau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mattia Perin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cris Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tay-ban-nha-doa-bat-ronaldo-tai-italia-188-191161.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ecda b\u1eaft Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo-180-191111.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191085.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4245","checkdouble":"191263"},{"date":"20:20 15/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/07: MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/17/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 1507 MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Bonucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 1507 MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Bonucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/tan-binh-thu-3-cua-mu-tri-gia-37-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Bonucci</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Star v\u00e0 Sunday Express, MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci c\u1ee7a AC Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bale quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>West Ham c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Felipe Anderson t\u1eeb Lazio, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 33.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Felipe Anderson \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Morata v\u00e0 Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 mua Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain se lai nhuong san khau cho Ronaldo\" title=\"Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Higuain&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Maurizio Sarri, mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n MU, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Koulibaly</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Kalidou Koulibaly, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Napoli, Koulibaly s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham nh\u1eafm Pavard thay Alderweireld&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Benjamin Pavard \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Toby Alderweireld. Hi\u1ec7n M.U \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Danny Ings</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Ings\" title=\"Danny Ings\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Southampton mu\u1ed1n chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Danny Ings</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Southampton ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-191262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/21/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-191262.html\">Southampton chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nSouthampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4244","checkdouble":"191267"},{"date":"19:54 15/07","title":"Southampton chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/21/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t r\u1ed9ng ra, t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Burnley, Ings ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanny Ings kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Roberto Firmino, The Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 sao tr\u1ebb Solanke v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sturridge, ngo\u00e0i ra Origi c\u0169ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ings tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/burnley-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-liverpool-172-189875.html\" target=\"_blank\">Burnley mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Danny Ings</span>, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t Southampton \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Danny Ings</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Southampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/20/danny-ings-thua-nhan-hoc-theo-firmino-de-lay-lai-phong-do-tot-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Southamptons chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Danny Ings</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Liverpool nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n trong tay Sturidge, Solanke v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Origi n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Danny Ings \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, n\u1ebfu Southampton h\u1ee9a trao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Liverpool t\u1eebng mua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Southampton, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4243","checkdouble":"191262"},{"date":"21:02 15/07","title":"HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Calum Chambers","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-unai-emery-muon-gay-soc-voi-truong-hop-cua-calum-chambers.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Calum Chambers ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Unai Emery, ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Calum Chambers</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Calum Chambers kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi Mustafi ho\u1eb7c Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Calum Chambers ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Calum Chambers ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/21/Calum-Chambers-phat-bieu-ve-Unai-Emery-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Calum Chambers</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Southampton trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-tinh-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-156792.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Chambers</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng c\u00f2n Per Mertesacker r\u1eddi CLB khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao Southampton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Calum Chambers ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Calum Chambers ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Unai Emery, ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery tinh de Chambers da tien ve o mua giai toi\" title=\"HLV Emery t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 Chambers \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/hlv-unai-emery-muon-gay-soc-voi-truong-hop-cua-calum-chambers.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 Chambers \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHLV n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00f4i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian th\u00edch nghi t\u00f4i tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn t\u1eeb HLV, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4242","checkdouble":"191264"},{"date":"21:15 15/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u201cv\u00f2i v\u0129nh\u201d Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Ph\u00e1p hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3, anh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1eaft r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc tay. Nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh cao g\u1ea7n 2m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua trong th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London khi kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, n\u01a1i 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi con v\u1eabn \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid li\u00ean t\u1ee5c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Courtois th\u1eddi gian qua. H\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf cho Keylor Navas \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi thu nh\u1eadp 200 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n cho Courtois song anh ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois co mot tran dau xuat sac\" title=\"Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Chelsea-muon-mua-Kasper-Schmeichel-thay-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 The Blues ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng cao thu nh\u1eadp cho m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Chelsea mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 g\u00ec\u201d, Courtois cho hay. \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng sau World Cup n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, Antonio Conte. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Courtois n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Dries Mertens (ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi Courtois tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9). Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 Sarri. V\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata-172-191241.html\">M\u1edbi t\u1edbi Chelsea, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d th\u1eddi Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4241","checkdouble":"191268"},{"date":"21:26 15/07","title":"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: MU v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/cuc-soc-mu-vang-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p Leicester.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fred</span> v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean Dalot. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-doi-hinh-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/8. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a M.U l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 bao g\u1ed3m Marouane Fellaini v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, Phil Jones, Ashley Young, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 g\u1eb7p Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c BTC Premier League</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/8, Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho\" title=\"Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/cuc-soc-mu-vang-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm h\u01a1n m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u c\u00f9ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 M.U. Pep v\u00e0 Pochettino c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f3 chung quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4240","checkdouble":"191269"},{"date":"21:39 15/07","title":"V\u00ec Sarri, Eden Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/vi-sarri-eden-hazard-co-the-o-lai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9 Dries Mertens v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard-180-191070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real li\u00ean t\u1ee5c h\u1ecfi mua Hazard</span>. Los Blancos v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Tuong-lai-Eden-Hazard-quyet-dinh-sau-cuoc-noi-chuyen-voi-Sarri-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eden Hazard ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNHM Chelsea c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n lo l\u1eafng khi Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 xem c\u00f3 n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i nghe th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cReal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bernabeu\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00ec HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9 Dries Mertens v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/vi-sarri-eden-hazard-co-the-o-lai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p Sarri v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDries Mertens \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 Sarri, anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi. Mertens c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Sarri, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4239","checkdouble":"191270"}]}